title: High Noon Dream
body:
I just woke up from a dream where I was versing High Noon Yasuo as Lux who also has a high noon skin.

She was in dark leather pants, had a cool cowboy hat and a short sheriffs duster.
Her wand was like a rattle snake.

I'm pretty sure Summoners Rift had a skin too because mid seemed a little dry and dusty.

Just thought I'd share. Dreams can be pretty cool.
